{"tid":1451892,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每個星期六日就一定訓唔到","createTime":"2019-08-11T21:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T22:27:01.000Z","uid":93540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8e75b41baa2f4c91a4902c4fffbc8860deb91722","tid":1451892,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:38:08.000Z","msg":"因為每個禮拜六日都有令人心痛同憤怒既事發生<br />\n啱啱睇左爆牙義士段片<br />\n真係好撚心痛 睇到好想喊<br />\n佢不斷大嗌 不斷叫唔好<br />\n一個後生仔點解要出黎受咁既苦 咪就係為左自由囉<br />\n用自己既前途冒險 換黎既比人抺黑做暴徒 收左錢搞事<br />\n黑警冇一個係無辜 死左都冇人可憐 話佢地係狗都侮辱左狗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"912e7fdda90e1a6b1ed10db24e13eb23072bb338","tid":1451892,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:46:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"47ad3ff6c8214baf7dc9dc4f8218fa31f7e53471","tid":1451892,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:46:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"563ff0b9147d4b274823a85d4ad3c14671d1ad38","tid":1451892,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:46:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"37ffd5667e1f5b1c7918e6a3c4f2a2bc35aa0909","tid":1451892,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:46:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1e52671a45c2751c928dafebe07c274179ecfba","tid":1451892,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:47:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d68b2ef5d8392c524f3b39a4236eee060d5d4620","tid":1451892,"u